Interface IDiagnosticEcuProps

    public interface IDiagnosticEcuProps
extends IEntity
    IDiagnosticEcuProps: Entity class of the tresosDB model.

    This meta-class is defined to gather diagnostic-related properties that apply in the scope of an entire ECU.

      • getSendRespPendOnTransToBoot

        boolean getSendRespPendOnTransToBoot()
        Query the value of the attribute SendRespPendOnTransToBoot.

        The purpose of this attribute is to define whether or not the ECU should send a NRC 0x78 (response pending) before transitioning to the bootloader (in this case the attribute shall be set to "true") or if the transition shall be initiated without sending NRC 0x78 (in this case the attribute shall be set to "false").

        Returns:
        The value or null
